Description
-----------

This function will perform a box filter on the specified normal map and
then normalize the result.

Usage
-----

    smoothnormals ([map])

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - The normal map to smooth.

Example
-------

Smooth normal map...

    textures/smoothed
    {
       {
          blend bumpmap
          map   smoothnormals(textures/custom/image_1.tga)
       }
    }

Notes
-----

None.

